cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and machine translation. Additionally, the use of neural architectures for this task suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The dataset extraction and manual evaluation aspects of the paper could also place it in the sub-categories of cs.SD (Sound) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval), respectively.
